                     <hi rend="largeCaps">EDWARD LAMPARD BOYDEN</hi>
                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18421128-5-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18421128-5-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18421128-5-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>for feloniously utter<lb></lb>ing, on the <rs id="t18421128-cd-4" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18421128-5-offence-1 t18421128-cd-4"></join>2nd of July</rs>, a forged acceptance to a bill of exchange for 25<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., knowing it to be forged, with intent to defraud <persName id="t18421128-name-109" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-109" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-109" type="surname" value="NATHAN"></interp>
